{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act35side", "eventName": "太陽甩在身後", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AS-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "文物也上班", "storyInfo": "在娜仁圖亞的哄騙下，祖拜爾被賣給拉恕爾。買賣結束後，拉恕爾的寵物開口講話，原來它們的真實身分是獸主。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g1_menatmainstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在等什麼？", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "電話。對你這樣上年紀的人來說，可能是有點新奇。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還要在這裡等多久？", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要懷疑，等就是了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一下能讓我接電話嗎？之前已經有人跟我講解過用法……", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不不，不行，你這個機械合成的嗓音一出聲，別人會當成詐騙電話的。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧。", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，按照你的說法，我們兩個的合作是對歷史上偉大同盟的效仿。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那請問，幫你跑腿找寶石對我有什麼好處？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，我確實有所收穫。昨天半夜你嚇到我的時候，我獲得了這隻飛到臉上的金拖鞋。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有什麼建議嗎？", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——不敢有，不敢有，我活著就是您最大的恩賜，您是薩爾貢的祖宗，帶著您尋找寶石是我該做的，您千萬別激動。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，贏得豐獲集會第一名的文物好像也是這麼一隻純金鑲藍寶石的拖鞋……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，它們應該恰好成對。", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "半夜在大街上尖叫擾民，也是一種發家手段？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……原本成對的文物，其中一件永遠沉進河底遺失，另一件自然也失去了大半價值。", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……請允許我好奇。這個時代的夢魘……都是像你這樣行事的嗎？", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你問倒我了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了搶劫、倒賣和綁架，我調查過各大部族的風俗和信仰，但真沒調查過我自己的出生地。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從某個清晨日出之後，我就再也沒回去過了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如此說來，你難道……正走在自己的天途上？", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天途？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（古老的語言）天途。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——不不不，我一點也不想聽到這個詞。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才不走天途，就算是我的老祖宗逼我也沒用。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道至今沒有踐行成年的儀式？！", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，又不是什麼重要的事情。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也許有一點夢魘的血統，但那幾滴血沒把我變成暴君和征服者，我也不打算讓它影響我自己的生活。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這很重要。", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若不走過天途，你的血要如何被你的先祖認可？", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，我的老祖宗們多半都失蹤在大地盡頭了，不會像你一樣突然從博物館裡坐起來罵我。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，那你呢？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說沙阿時代的人們會在成年時剃個光頭，然後塗上香膏。但又有人說，所謂的“香膏”其實很難聞……我超好奇的。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也……", "name": "祖拜爾"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，等到了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ringoff"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "group_interclude_vertical_common", "size": "290,760", "style": 0.0, "offset": "250,0", "channel": 3.0, "tsfrom": "0,1", "tsto": "1,1", "tsduration": 0.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "false", "pfrom": "270,0", "pto": "270,0", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……怎樣，這麼快就有寶石的消息了嗎？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "true", "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "270,0", "pto": "270,0", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，女士，十分巧合，剛剛寶石交易所的監管人放出消息，他手中有一塊寶石正待交易，各方面都符合您的描述。", "name": "寶石掮客"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false", "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "270,0", "pto": "270,0", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我要直接去見他。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "true", "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "270,0", "pto": "270,0", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是……即使有我從中介紹，你也很難直接和監管人談這筆交易。", "name": "寶石掮客"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false", "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "270,0", "pto": "270,0", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？我聽我手下說，她們直接找前台就能賣寶石。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "true", "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "270,0", "pto": "270,0", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "賣倒是容易，買就不一樣了。寶石交易所並不是一般的商鋪，你需要拿出夠份量的砝碼，才能從監管人手上直接拿到東西。", "name": "寶石掮客"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false", "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "pfrom": "270,0", "pto": "270,0", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠份量的砝碼？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我有個想法。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"clear": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g10_grandbazaar_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#7$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉恕爾"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，是的，這就是我想談的生意。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "近期正在博物館展出的古屍……沙阿時代的無名將領。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶石交易所年輕的監管人神情複雜地看了她一眼，然後在巨大的鍍金箱子前俯下身。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖拜爾以雙手交疊胸前的姿態，寧靜地平躺著。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平心而論，娜仁圖亞認為這是祖拜爾最有價值的時刻，連那駭人的黃金面具都彷彿散發出了神聖的柔光。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個箱子很眼熟。", "name": "拉恕爾"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是從博物館原樣搬出來的棺材……的仿製品，仿製品。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chopsteeltube", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……（輕輕敲打祖拜爾的身軀）", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#2$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（用手電筒檢查胸腔內部）", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#3$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，這可不是一般的文物，你下手輕點，別這麼不專業。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我聽說它已經復活了，能夠自如行動。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個嘛，我們都知道人死不能復生，都是源石技藝表演而已。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，如果它真的會動，你不害怕嗎？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怕我買下來之後它又自己逃走嗎？", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "娜仁圖亞", "content": "這個嘛……"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "娜仁圖亞", "content": "哎呀，那隻黑色的動物是你的寵物？哈哈，真美啊！"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不愧是寶石交易所的監管人，掌握整座城市金錢流通的人，連寵物都如此與眾不同。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#6$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）沃奧，是他嗎？", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嗅探）", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（在棺材旁坐下）", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，你看，牠聞出來了，這種死了上千年的氣味是不可能偽造的。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我跟你做交易的誠意也是半點不摻假的。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，我知道這件文物太過珍貴，就算對你來說也沒那麼容易處理——對，我是甩了個麻煩給你，所以我不指望能賺太多。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我保證博物館沒辦法查到我……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你給出了很重的砝碼。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是遠沒有到我的秤無法衡量的程度。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊，好。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#10$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想交換什麼？我聽說你是為一顆寶石來的。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，本來是這樣，但來的路上我有了個新想法，那顆寶石我不需要了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是外來的，給我金條就行。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赤金結算？我去拿適合的秤。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩你先把貨物移進裡間，免得被其他人看到。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……合作愉快？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g12_gemexchange", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，我就喜歡這麼爽快的人！", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一點也不喜歡睡回這個棺材的感覺。你其實沒必要讓你的手下特地把它運出來。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓，你別說話……稍微再忍一下，我很快就回來接你。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你抓緊時間，在今天之內找到你要的那顆寶石。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，千萬別忘了。我還找你有事。", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_goldbarhit"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我的報價，你意下如何？", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……♪忘不了刀刃上的月牙，少年的真心洗成黃金♪", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是忘不了……沒意見，完全沒意見！", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我就離開啦。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請便。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（對祖拜爾眨眨眼睛）", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#5$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（對娜仁圖亞眨眨眼睛）", "name": "祖拜爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#2$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "期待我們的下次合作！", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#7$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒說還有下次。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#7$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g10_grandbazaar_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，我也沒說還有下次。至少短期內絕不會有。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個老東西還想指使我幫他跑腿？抱歉，永別了！", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#7$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g12_gemexchan